MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2008-0919. Cincinnati City School Dist. Bd. of Edn. v. State Bd. of Edn.

Hamilton App. No. C-070084, 176 Ohio App.3d 678, 2008-Ohio-2845. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Hamilton County. Upon consideration of appellants’ application for dismissal,

It is ordered by the court that the application for dismissal is granted. Accordingly, this cause is dismissed.
